snippet.title: Infect Cam - Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Ready to write your own survival story? Infect Cam takes you on a thrilling adventure where danger lurks at every corner. In a world overrun by zombies, use your skills to survive, gather resources, plan your strategies, and face your enemies head-on!

Wishlist Now: [https://store.steampowered.com/app/3168930/Infect_Cam/]
